2026-05-16T02:50:45.5492198Z 13    <!--
2026-05-16T02:50:45.5492747Z 14        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-05-16T02:50:45.5493586Z 15        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
