2026-05-16T02:50:46.0979417Z 12    <!--
2026-05-16T02:50:46.0979781Z 13        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-05-16T02:50:46.0980118Z 14        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
