2026-05-16T02:50:46.1006318Z 51    <!--
2026-05-16T02:50:46.1006639Z 52        Foreground service used to keep the Pomodoro countdown alive when
2026-05-16T02:50:46.1006955Z 53        the app is backgrounded. Without this, a viewModelScope coroutine
2026-05-16T02:50:46.1007269Z 54        is cancelled as soon as the user switches apps and the completion
2026-05-16T02:50:46.1007559Z 55        notification is never shown. The timer is declared as a
2026-05-16T02:50:46.1007906Z 56        mediaPlayback foreground service because Samsung One UI suppresses
2026-05-16T02:50:46.1008235Z 57        FOREGROUND_SERVICE_SPECIAL_USE notifications, preventing the
